Field Detail

state

protected volatile char state
Holds the current Thread state. 
                U = Unknown
                S = Started
                R - Running a client
                I = Idle
                L = Looking for client
                P = Was sent back to pool
                W = Waiting in pool		
                N = Was notified, Looking for client
                D = Dead
